02:37.736 --> 02:40.446
<i>There are almost 10 million
telephone exchange lines.</i>

02:40.905 --> 02:43.156
<i>Over 50 phone services.</i>

02:43.407 --> 02:46.366
<i>3 million New Yorkers
are cell phone users.</i>

02:46.576 --> 02:49.789
<i>It used to be a mark of insanity
to see people talk to themselves.</i>

02:50.246 --> 02:55.626
<i>Now it's a mark of status. And speed dial
is quickly replacing the drop of a coin.</i>

02:55.835 --> 02:58.506
<i>Despite increased usage
of cellular devices...</i>

02:58.715 --> 03:02.300
<i>... an estimated 4.5 million residents
and 2 million visitors...</i>

03:02.509 --> 03:06.678
